preserve

clear
insheet using "labels.csv", names 

sort name

local i = 0
levelsof name, local(level)
foreach v1 of local level {
   local i = `i' + 1
   local v = name[`i']
   local lab_`v' = label[`i']
   display label[`i']
}

restore


foreach v of varlist * {
  if ( "`lab_`v''" ~= "" ) {
  	label var `v' "`lab_`v''"
        notes `v':"`lab_`v''"
  }
}

* eof
